tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE advertising_revenue (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    client_id INT,
    revenue_amount DECIMAL,
    revenue_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE campaign_metrics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  impressions INT,
  clicks INT,
  conversion_rate DECIMAL,
  cost DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE campaign_performance_metrics (
 id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 impressions INT,
 clicks INT,
 conversions INT,
 revenue DECIMAL
 );

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
 id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 name VARCHAR(50),
 start_date DATE,
 end_date DATE,
 client_id INT
 );
